394
00:25:48.035 --> 00:25:51.153
Now. you gotta tell me
what is happening now!

395
00:25:51.155 --> 00:25:53.798
- That's not your concern.
- Oh. come on!

396
00:25:54.639 --> 00:25:56.959
Listen to me... you
are not blowing me off

397
00:25:56.961 --> 00:25:59.366
