end of the story" crap!

398
00:25:59.368 --> 00:26:00.682
Now. just specifics!

399
00:26:00.684 --> 00:26:03.445
You're asking for
information you can't have.

400
00:26:14.281 --> 00:26:16.283
If anything happens to her...

401
00:26:20.743 --> 00:26:23.023
I can't do this.

402
00:26:23.025 --> 00:26:25.027
I can't.

403
00:26:27.790 --> 00:26:31.952
Hm. Hm.

404
00:26:31.954 --> 00:26:34.234
Alright.

405
00:26:34.236 --> 00:26:36.278
Alright.

406
00:26:37.679 --> 00:26:41.000
Now. you listen. and you shut up.

407
00:26:41.002 --> 00:26:43.282
This man has other things on his mind.

408
00:26:43.284 --> 00:26:45.446
He's not thinking about you.

409
00:26:48.289 --> 00:26:51.810
Lalo Salamanca is going to die.

410
00:26:51.812 --> 00:26:53.412
Tonight.

411
00:26:55.616 --> 00:26:57.055
Tonight... ?

412
00:26:57.057 --> 00:27:00.138
This time tomorrow. it'll be done.

413
00:27:05.025 --> 00:27:07.585
Oh. Okay. then...

414
00:27:09.589 --> 00:27:13.794
Now... I need you to leave.

415
00:27:15.114 --> 00:27:19.038
I have family coming over.

416
00:28:16.011 --> 00:28:17.250
Charlie Manson!

417
00:28:25.580 --> 00:28:29.302
Don Eladio.

418
00:28:36.775 --> 00:28:37.799
Bolsa.

419
00:28:41.075 --> 00:28:42.198
Hey.

420
00:28:57.810 --> 00:28:59.210
- Ah.
- Hmm.

421
00:28:59.212 --> 00:29:01.276
- Excelente.
- Sí.

422
00:29:15.787 --> 00:29:17.971
Mm. Hm.

423
00:29:33.163 --> 00:29:35.644
Ooh. I "Magnum. P.I."!

424
00:29:43.693 --> 00:29:46.294
¿Eh. Bolsa?

425
00:29:47.537 --> 00:29:49.561
Sí.

426
00:29:57.106 --> 00:29:58.430
Don.

427
00:30:01.990 --> 00:30:03.714
Ah.

428
00:30:12.881 --> 00:30:14.905
"Frunk".

429
00:30:18.686 --> 00:30:20.510
Oh.

430
00:30:32.940 --> 00:30:35.444
Oiga. Don Eladio...

431
00:30:42.495 --> 00:30:44.518
Ah.

432
00:30:57.202 --> 00:31:00.227
Ah.

433
00:31:17.661 --> 00:31:19.701
Entonces...

434
00:31:31.995 --> 00:31:33.474
Mm.

435
00:31:33.476 --> 00:31:34.836
Ah.

436
00:32:04.625 --> 00:32:06.345
Bikers?

437
00:32:12.433 --> 00:32:14.577
Hm.

438
00:32:27.781 --> 00:32:31.047
Don Eladio...

439
00:32:38.938 --> 00:32:40.962
Mm-hmm.

440
00:32:59.597 --> 00:33:03.802
