451
00:34:55.616 --> 00:34:58.057
He's not gonna tell me. but he knows.

452
00:34:58.059 --> 00:34:59.538
And you believe him?

453
00:34:59.540 --> 00:35:02.100
Yeah. I do.

454
00:35:02.102 --> 00:35:05.303
