488
00:37:19.591 --> 00:37:23.833
So. I ran into Howard
at the courthouse today.

489
00:37:26.197 --> 00:37:27.797
Yeah?

490
00:37:27.799 --> 00:37:31.240
Told me something about

491
00:37:31.242 --> 00:37:33.883
