00:37:46.247 --> 00:37:47.750
For what it's worth.

495
00:37:47.752 --> 00:37:49.537
that all happened before we...

496
00:37:49.539 --> 00:37:51.299
Before we got married?

497
00:37:51.301 --> 00:37:52.660
Yeah.

498
00:37:57.321 --> 00:38:01.549
