502
00:38:12.401 --> 00:38:14.481
It's...

503
00:38:14.483 --> 00:38:16.443
I-It's... It's all about him...

504
00:38:16.445 --> 00:38:19.886
it's always all about him.

505
00:38:19.888 --> 00:38:23.809
The guy is in love with himself.

506
00:38:23.811 --> 00:38:27.293
He needed to be taken down a peg.

507
00:38:27.295 --> 00:38:31.500
So...

508
00:38:32.980 --> 00:38:35.420
