509
00:38:36.170 --> 00:38:37.553
You went after his car.

510
00:38:37.555 --> 00:38:42.147
You went after his reputation. So...

511
00:38:42.149 --> 00:38:46.394
I think maybe the next thing is...

512
00:38:46.396 --> 00:38:50.601
his hair. right?

513
00:38:51.357 --> 00:38:54.640
Suppose... and I'm... I'm
just brainstorming here...

514
00:38:54.642 --> 00:38:57.881
