529
00:39:34.838 --> 00:39:37.118
- so that...
- Bleaches his hair and his eyebrows

530
00:39:37.120 --> 00:39:38.960
- and everything.
- Yes. yes. and the eyebrows.

531
00:39:42.044 --> 00:39:44.147
Or... Or...

532
00:39:44.149 --> 00:39:48.249
Or we break into his house.

533
00:39:48.251 --> 00:39:51.518
replace all the fluffy
toilet-paper rolls

534
00:39:51.520 --> 00:39:53.534
